</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="106" pageNumber="384" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="106.[179,1385,291,642]" pageId="106" pageNumber="384">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[182,539,448,481]" pageId="106" pageNumber="384">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Critically Endangered on The IUCN Red List. It has a small extent of occurrence (43 km?) and there is continuing decline in the number of mature individuals.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
